Package: brclimr
Title: Fetch Zonal Statistics of Weather Indicators for Brazilian Municipalities
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Raphael", "Saldanha", , "raphael.de-freitas-saldanha@inria.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-0652-8466"))
Description: Fetches zonal statistics of weather indicators created for each Brazilian municipality. Datasets of zonal statistics were created using data from the 'BR-DWGD' and 'TerraClimate' projects as sources. For each municipality and weather indicator, zonal statistics were calculated considering the data cells that intersect the municipality. 
